Use the standard library
This is how to int_to_bin of n:
   When n is 0, then:
      The answer is "0"
   End when
   Remember that result is ""
   Remember that x is n
   Do this 1000 times:
      When x is 0, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      Remember that bit is remainder of x and 2
      Remember that result is "{bit}{result}"
      Remember that x is quotient of x and 2
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know
>>> int_to_bin of 0 
"0"
>>> int_to_bin of 1 
"1"
>>> int_to_bin of 2 
"10"
>>> int_to_bin of 3 
"11"
>>> int_to_bin of 11 
"1011"
>>> int_to_bin of 255 
"11111111"
>>> int_to_bin of 256 
"100000000"
>>> int_to_bin of 10 
"1010"